AGI - Last week, the United States has for the first time since the beginning of the Gaza conflict blocked an American manufacturing ammunition shipment intended for Israel. It is an apparent proof of Washington's growing insufficiency for the attitude of the Netanyahu government in the Gaza conflict. It was revealed by the US Axios website, citing Israeli officials, taken over by the international press.
&nbsp;
The pressure on the White House is growing, even for protests in American universities. Only last Friday, tens of democratic elect in Congress asked President Joe Biden in a letter to consider the suspension of arms sales to Israel if he does not change his approach.
